formula_175

For finite &quot;n&quot;, the estimator for formula_17 is unbiased, but the one for formula_18 is biased. As for the normal distribution, an unbiased estimator for formula_18 can be obtained by replacing the denominator &quot;n&quot; by &quot;n&quot;−1 in the equation for formula_179.

From this, the MLE for the expectancy of x is:
